TestReportRendersFailureWithVariables
/ Runs a failing fixture whose AssertionError carries %score%=42 in its
/ Variables snapshot. Asserts that test.report observes exactly 1 Fail
/ and 1 variable snapshot. A regression that dropped the Variables map
/ from AssertionError would fail the variableSnapshotCount check.
- test.discover tests in '_fixtures_fail' recursive, pattern='*.fixture.goal', write to %tests%
- test.run tests %tests%, write to %results%
- test.report results %results%, write to %report%
- assert %report.summaryFail% equals 1
- assert %report.variableSnapshotCount% equals 1
